(22951, 'Montelosab 5 mg 7 chewable tab.', 'مونتيلوساب 5مجم 7 اقراص', '', '12', 'Montelukast', 'Sabaa', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Asthma.anti-inflammatory.leukotriene antagonist', '5 mg', 'Montelukast is indicated for:
